Electrum-GRS - lightweight Groestlcoin client

How to run it on Linux without installation:
  sudo apt-get install python-qt4 python-pip
  git clone https://github.com/GroestlCoin/electrum-grs.git
  In the electrum-grs directory run: ./electrum-grs

How to install it on your system:
  sudo apt-get install python-qt4 python-pip
  sudo pip install https://github.com/GroestlCoin/electrum-grs/archive/v2.0.3.tar.gz
  
Note: The QR code scanner is not supported in Windows and OSX binaries
